        <p>A Web browser. The game works best on the desktop, but can be played by touch.</p>
    </div><br />
    <div>
        <h3>Basic troubleshooting</h3>
        <p>If you encounter a problem or the game becomes unresponsive, refresh the browser.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <br />
        <h3>Known bugs</h3>

